{"tid":1279031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"夢還未醒 如何能令行動昇華","createTime":"2019-07-02T14:42:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T14:47:05.000Z","uid":273012,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8f7f2e0631978d5f6cb62d7edf3c6a434aab5e76","tid":1279031,"uid":273012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:42:21.000Z","msg":"不分化 不割蓆 不灰 <br />\n但不代表不反思 <br />\n直至今時今日 緊抱五大訴求 係米足夠 <br />\n有人覺得失焦 政府藍絲覺得已回應訴求  <br />\n行動到底應該點走落去  <br />\n<br />\n我第一次出POST  我係一個9 0後嘅中大生 當年佔中坐係夏愨道温書 訓過街 <br />\n612 623 都有出黎 <br />\n我係典型企係勇武派後面嘅大眾 <br />\n琴日當值完去遊行 留到夜晚頂唔住要番去 <br />\n但番到去都係訓唔著 睇到好想喊 <br />\n雖然我認為衝立法會冇咩用 但我同你地係同路人 <br />\n我唔想呢場運動比人用暴動一句就打落水  <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要繼續 就要昇華</span></span> </strong><br />\n<br />\n暴行係一個表象 我地要強調「還政於民」 <br />\n君不見 各大民調表示反對逃犯條例修訂人數過半 [1,2] 大律師公會發聲 [3] 數十萬人上街 <br />\n林鄭依然一句「如常開會二讀」 呢個係赤裸裸嘅獨裁主義 <br />\n<br />\n君不見 一眾建制明知條例有問題 但都要硬著頭皮通過 <br />\n呢個係議會失去功用的嘅鐵證 <br />\n<br />\n我地要舉出<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">證據</span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>證明制度嘅崩壞  </strong></span></span><br />\n強調用以制衡政府嘅議會失效 <br />\n強調與其靠林鄭聽民意 不如改變制度 讓人民對政府能夠作出規限  <br />\n<br />\n只有有效嘅制度去讓<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人民發聲</span></strong> <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人民作主</span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">社會先會減少暴行遊行示威</span></span></strong>  <br />\n一定要比佢地知道  <br />\n<br />\n第二個崩壞嘅制度係監警制度  <br />\n根據2017/2018年監警會報告 [4]，2872宗指控個案，419宗無法證實，893宗無法追查。[5] 佔旺事件274項指控，171項（62%）沒法追查，27宗無法證實（10%）。就2016年農年新年旺角騷亂，時任《明報》記者鄧先生投訴在採訪期間被警員襲擊，事隔逾兩年，仍未有結果。  [6]<br />\n<br />\n我地要FACT CHECK出足夠嘅證據，指責制度嘅無力，<br />\n要成立獨立調查調查會去改變監警權崩壞嘅制度  <br />\n<br />\n所以 行動要昇華 我地要<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">比所有人睇到制度嘅問題 </span></strong><br />\n唔係靠口號 唔只靠衝 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">靠嘅係證據 同埋宣傳</span></strong> 最好係街站<br />\n要所有人都睇到香港係處於<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">危急存亡之秋 </span> </strong><br />\n<br />\n最後 我想講嘅係 <br />\n要反思點樣唔變做暴民政治 要諗清楚做呢樣野嘅原則目的 <br />\n佔領立會係迫政府回應的話 衝左入去 入到去噴字同埋留守已經好夠 <br />\n打爆閉路電視 螢幕之類有冇必要同作用 有冇反作用 要諗清楚  <br />\n<br />\n堅守靈台一片清明 認清目標 先能夠無愧於心 不留人話柄  <br />\n希望連登繼續成為大家反思 進步嘅平台 讓全世界睇到我地嘅民主決心  <br />\n<br />\nReferene<br />\n1. 港大民調 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkupop.hku.hk/chinese/report/singming_extradition_bill/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkupop.hku.hk%2Fchinese%2Freport%2Fsingming_extradition_bill%2F&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRc2lERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=a10cac29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkupop.hku.hk/chinese/report/singming_extradition_bill/</a> 明報委任中大民調 <br />\n<br />\n2.「明報民調：逃犯例草案 近半人反對 若有港人港審 逾半人支持」2019年6月7日 <a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20190607/s00001/1559846278380/%E6%98%8E%E5%A0%B1%E6%B0%91%E8%AA%BF-%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E4%BE%8B%E8%8D%89%E6%A1%88-%E8%BF%91%E5%8D%8A%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D-%E8%8B%A5%E6%9C%89%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%B8%AF%E5%AF%A9-%E9%80%BE%E5%8D%8A%E4%BA%BA%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190607%2Fs00001%2F1559846278380%2F%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25AA%25BF-%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E4%25BE%258B%25E8%258D%2589%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%258D%258A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D-%25E8%258B%25A5%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25AF%25A9-%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%258D%258A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRc2lERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=6164554f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190607%2Fs00001%2F1559846278380%2F%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25AA%25BF-%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E4%25BE%258B%25E8%258D%2589%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%258D%258A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D-%25E8%258B%25A5%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25AF%25A9-%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%258D%258A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581&h=0c743a9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20190607/s00001/1559846278380/%E6%98%8E%E5%A0%B1%E6%B0%91%E8%AA%BF-%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E4%BE%8B%E8%8D%89%E6%A1%88-%E8%BF%91%E5%8D%8A%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D-%E8%8B%A5%E6%9C%89%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%B8%AF%E5%AF%A9-%E9%80%BE%E5%8D%8A%E4%BA%BA%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81</a>  <br />\n<br />\n3. 香港大律師公會<br />\n關於《2019 年逃犯及刑事事宜相互法律協助法例（修訂）條例草案》（下稱「該草案」）的簡易指南<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkba.org/sites/default/files/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%83%20%E9%97%9C%E6%96%BC%E3%80%8A2019%20%E5%B9%B4%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E5%8F%8A%E5%88%91%E4%BA%8B%E4%BA%8B%E5%AE%9C%E7%9B%B8%E4%BA%92%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E5%8D%94%E5%8A%A9%E6%B3%95%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%88%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%EF%BC%89%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E8%8D%89%E6%A1%88%E3%80%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%B0%A1%E6%98%93%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkba.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%2520%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%2596%25BC%25E3%2580%258A2019%2520%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E5%258F%258A%25E5%2588%2591%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%25AE%259C%25E7%259B%25B8%25E4%25BA%2592%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%258A%25A9%25E6%25B3%2595%25E4%25BE%258B%25EF%25BC%2588%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E8%25A8%2582%25EF%25BC%2589%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E8%258D%2589%25E6%25A1%2588%25E3%2580%258B%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%25B0%25A1%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%258D%2597.pdf&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRc2lERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=4002e068\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkba.org/sites/default/files/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%83%20%E9%97%9C%E6%96%BC%E3%80%8A2019%20%E5%B9%B4%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E5%8F%8A%E5%88%91%E4%BA%8B%E4%BA%8B%E5%AE%9C%E7%9B%B8%E4%BA%92%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E5%8D%94%E5%8A%A9%E6%B3%95%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%88%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%EF%BC%89%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E8%8D%89%E6%A1%88%E3%80%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%B0%A1%E6%98%93%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 2017/2018年監警會報告 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ipcc.gov.hk/tc/publications/annual_report/2017.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipcc.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublications%2Fannual_report%2F2017.html&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRc2lERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=2d916807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ipcc.gov.hk/tc/publications/annual_report/2017.html</a>  <br />\n<br />\n5. 2016年監警會與投訴及內部調查科 聯席會議公開部分 <a href=\"https://www.ipcc.gov.hk/doc/tc/meetings/20161219.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipcc.gov.hk%2Fdoc%2Ftc%2Fmeetings%2F20161219.pdf&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRc2lERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=1480f406\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ipcc.gov.hk/doc/tc/meetings/20161219.pdf</a>  <br />\n<br />\n6. 香港01 新聞 「投訴警察今年首兩個月212宗 六成涉疏忽職守 4宗捏造證據」2018年3月 <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/170199/%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%96%E5%85%A9%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88212%E5%AE%97-%E5%85%AD%E6%88%90%E6%B6%89%E7%96%8F%E5%BF%BD%E8%81%B7%E5%AE%88-4%E5%AE%97%E6%8D%8F%E9%80%A0%E8%AD%89%E6%93%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F170199%2F%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588212%25E5%25AE%2597-%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%25B6%2589%25E7%2596%258F%25E5%25BF%25BD%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%25AE%2588-4%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%258D%258F%25E9%2580%25A0%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2593%259A&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRc2lERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=f2c2249b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/170199/%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%96%E5%85%A9%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88212%E5%AE%97-%E5%85%AD%E6%88%90%E6%B6%89%E7%96%8F%E5%BF%BD%E8%81%B7%E5%AE%88-4%E5%AE%97%E6%8D%8F%E9%80%A0%E8%AD%89%E6%93%9A</a>  <br />\n<br />\n後記:<br />\n- 林鄭下台 作用不大 問題在於制度 一日冇野制衡政府 所有特首都只會聽命北京而唔係人民 所以林鄭下唔下台 根本唔係重點  <br />\n2. 我認為今屆政府已經冇左再推「逃犯條例修訂」嘅心，所以「徹回」呢個字眼其實不重要。重點在於，點樣避免建制再一次肓撐政府，係問題議案上面漠視民意，只跟中央指示。所以重點都係有問題嘅議會。 <br />\n<br />\n聚焦民意 <br />\nTime for change"},{"pid":"61b3a85ed42349676bd04c2aa0177bc2b094d5f8","tid":1279031,"uid":46758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:43:36.000Z","msg":"true"},{"pid":"ec195e793dbb8d6e3caa0f4f472fcbd663da32f7","tid":1279031,"uid":261813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:43:57.000Z","msg":"「思想改革運動」任何人請睇一睇，需大量文宣工作<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dddgCS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dddgCS</a><br />\n<br />\n我意見"},{"pid":"82f3fa957138cb199dc4d83f19a68f4b6f1fff44","tid":1279031,"uid":273012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:44:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a39a2b39417dd9eb480cfab073229f31b83f95d5","tid":1279031,"uid":273012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:47:05.000Z","msg":"push"}]}